verbose_text: To determine whether TNF-alpha activated NF-kappaB signaling in human neuroblastoma SH-SY5Y cells, SH-SY5Y neuroblastoma cells were cultured in the presence of 20 ng/ml TNF-alpha for the indicated time and subsequently the total cell lysates were collected and subjected to western blot analysis for NF-kappaB (p65), phosphorylated-IkappaB-alpha and IkappaB-alpha.
